CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,FA runner from London has become the
OL,8,Ffirst person in the world to complete
OL,9,F1,000 parkruns.
OL,11,FDarren Wood was given a guard of
OL,12,Fhonour from his fellow Sutton Runners
OL,13,Fas he approached the finish line to
OL,14,Fachieve his milestone on a warm, sunny
OL,15,Fday at Morden parkrun in south London,
OL,16,Fsurrounded by friends and family.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,FA stream of well-wishers took turns to
OL,8,Fcongratulate Mr Wood and have photos
OL,9,Ftaken with him before and after the
OL,10,Fevent and he was presented with a
OL,11,Fyellow 1,000 parkrun T-shirt, a cape
OL,12,Fand a crown as he was dubbed "the king
OL,13,Fof parkrun".
OL,15,FMr Wood, 43, from Carshalton, south
OL,16,FLondon, first took part in October
OL,17,F2004 and has regularly participated in
OL,18,Fthe free weekly event ever since.
OL,26,@tD@^OUuD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
