OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,FHe has run at 119 different parkruns
OL,8,Fin seven countries and has also
OL,9,Fvolunteered 415 times at the 5k or a
OL,10,F2k junior parkrun.
OL,12,FParkrun started on Saturday October 2
OL,13,F2004 as the Bushy Park Time Trial when
OL,14,F13 runners joined a free timed 5k run
OL,15,Fin south-west London which was
OL,16,Forganised by runner Paul Sinton-Hewitt
OL,17,Fwhile he was recovering from injury.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,FThere are now 913 different parkrun
OL,8,Flocations in 23 countries and more
OL,9,Fthan four million people have taken
OL,10,Fpart.
OL,12,FJunior parkruns take place on Sundays
OL,13,Fin the UK, Ireland and Australia.Like
OL,14,FMr Sinton-Hewitt, Mr Wood was a member
OL,15,Fof south-west London running club
OL,16,FRanelagh Harriers but he skipped the
OL,17,Ffirst event, thinking he was not fast
OL,18,Fenough to take part in a time trial.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,FHe joined in the following Saturday
OL,8,Fand told the Press Association: "For
OL,9,Fme it's a habit, I just rock up every
OL,10,Fweek and I just do it.
OL,12,F"I love getting out and exploring new
OL,13,Fparkruns and meeting new communities."
OL,15,FMr Wood, who is 36 parkruns ahead of
OL,16,Fhis closest rival, said the attention
OL,17,Faround being the first to 1,000 has
OL,18,Fbeen "a little bit overwhelming", but
OL,19,Fadded: "It's just a nice celebration.
OL,21,F"I don't want the limelight.
OL,26,@pD@aOUtD@AOUuD@fO]zD@FOUzD@`O]{D@HOU}D@
OL,26,AAOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,F"This is about a celebration of
OL,8,Fparkrun.
OL,10,F"Just because I've been the first
OL,11,Fperson to get there, it could have
OL,12,Fbeen anyone."
OL,14,FHe added: "This milestone isn't about
OL,15,Fme, it's about the parkrun community
OL,16,Fand what parkrun is doing for everyone.
OL,18,F"Parkrun is inclusive for everyone.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUtD@MO]vD@KOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,F"Everyone is welcome and it will
OL,8,Fchange and save lives if we can get
OL,9,Fmore and more people involved.
OL,11,F"I'd love for others who have never
OL,12,Fbeen part of a parkrun to just pick up
OL,13,Fthe courage to attend their first
OL,14,Fevent and be there.
OL,16,F"Because parkrun has changed and saved
OL,17,Fmy life and it will do that for
OL,18,Fothers, I would almost guarantee that."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
