OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,FMr Wood struggled with his mental
OL,8,Fhealth and self-harmed when his
OL,9,Fmarriage ended and he faced debt and
OL,10,Fproblems at work.
OL,12,FWhen he went to parkrun "everything
OL,13,Ffelt normal", he said, adding: "I
OL,14,Fwasn't judged any more, I could just
OL,15,Fbe me and I could talk to people and
OL,16,Fexplain how I was feeling."
OL,26,@tD@YOUuD@LO]uD@`OUxD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,FMr Wood is using the interest in his
OL,8,Fmilestone run to encourage other
OL,9,Fpeople who are struggling to seek
OL,10,Fsupport, saying: "I'm doing this to
OL,11,Fhopefully save a life.
OL,13,F"If I can save somebody's else's life,
OL,14,Fthat's all I want out of this."
OL,16,FHe added: "My key message would be
OL,17,Fthat it's important for people to talk
OL,18,Fand not to feel judged.
OL,20,F"I felt hopeless but I came across as
OL,21,Fbeing the happiest person around.
OL,26,@rD@ROUuD@AOUvD@_O]xD@KOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,F"We are all very good at hiding how we
OL,8,Ffeel.
OL,10,F"If there's one thing, be kind because
OL,11,Fyou never know what somebody else is
OL,12,Fgoing through."
OL,14,FMr Wood urged others to try parkrun,
OL,15,Fsaying: "Go and try it, you will not
OL,16,Fcome away disappointed. Just build up
OL,17,Fthat courage.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUtD@OO]wD@IOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,F"Understand that you will not be
OL,8,Fjudged, everyone is welcome, it
OL,9,Fdoesn't matter how fast or slow you
OL,10,Fare.
OL,12,F"Nobody is going to look at you funny
OL,13,Fbecause you are new to it.
OL,15,F"Everyone is welcome. There's always a
OL,16,Ffirst timers briefing so if you don't
OL,17,Fknow the course, you're going to a new
OL,18,Fcourse, you are made to feel welcome.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,F"That's the nice thing about parkrun,
OL,8,Fyou've got the tailwalker so nobody's
OL,9,Fgoing to come last."Register online,
OL,10,Fget your barcode and just rock up.
OL,12,F"It's free, it's for everyone, what's
OL,13,Fnot to like?"
OL,15,FMr Wood plans to continue his parkrun
OL,16,Fhabit.
OL,18,F"I'm going to aim big, I'm aiming for
OL,19,F2,000 in another 20 years," he said,
OL,20,Flaughing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@TOUtD@AOUuD@MO]zD@AOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780409469
OL,3,CRunner from London becomes first
OL,4,Cperson in world to complete 1,000
OL,5,Cparkruns
OL,7,F"Aim high, you've got to be positive,
OL,8,Fyou've got to have big dreams.
OL,10,F"Whether I get there or not is another
OL,11,Fmatter, but aim big.
OL,13,F"Tour a little bit more, get round a
OL,14,Ffew other places, enjoy it, go on lots
OL,15,Fof adventures, this is what it's all
OL,16,Fabout.
OL,18,F"About giving back as well, getting up
OL,19,Fto 500 volunteers as well."I'd love to
OL,20,Fdo more volunteering."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU{D@[OU|D@VO]
